description: This file defines a Confluence connector object for a frontend application, including methods for searching, creating pages, starting OAuth, and disconnecting from Confluence.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Performs a search query against Confluence pages, returning an array of normalized items.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Creates a new Confluence page with the given payload.

methods.name: startOAuth
methods.description: Initiates OAuth login process with Confluence.

methods.name: disconnect
methods.description: Disconnects or removes the Confluence connection.
